title: Katy Garbi Complete Discography (1989-2013)
description:
I don't own most of this,most of it got from several sources.I just gathered all and sorted.
I changed a LOT of metadata and filenames to keep it consistent and clean,and put some cover images.
Quality is OK overall,most of it is MP3,ranges from 128kbps-320kbps.

This also contains remixes.I'm not sure if I missed some song(nobody's perfect),
but this should be a complete discography so far(Katy is still active singer).

I have a somewhat slow upload,so it would mean a lot if you people would seed after you finish this.

Enjoy.
--
Vozho
